(150, 1, '2017-03-20 08:18:55', '2017-03-20 08:18:55', 'Yes you will be able to get your capital back provided your investment has reached maturity. Depending on the amount you invest, you can withdraw your capital plus all interest accrued in 25 - 180 days. You can also keep your investment (SH) active to earn more interest. You can withdraw your interest whenever you want.', 'Will PreBit return my Capital/Principal?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'will-prebit-return-my-capitalprincipal', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:54:53', '2017-03-22 05:54:53', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=150', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(151, 1, '2017-03-20 08:19:07', '2017-03-20 08:19:07', 'Please first download PreBit introduction <a href=\"http://pre-bit.org/readme.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a> and <a href=\"http://pre-bit.org/instruction.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a> for the instruction. They are extremely important for you to get started.\r\nWithin the PreBit community, we say \"Send Help\" instead of invest. After adding funds to your Bitcoin wallet on PreBit (we call it PreBit wallet), click on Send Help menu and put an amount you are willing to give to the community. Please note that if you have not invested yet, you can take the money out of your PreBit wallet whenever your want.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'How do I invest on PreBit?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-invest-on-prebit', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:53:34', '2017-03-22 05:53:34', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=151', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(152, 1, '2017-03-20 08:19:25', '2017-03-20 08:19:25', 'In order to withdraw Bitcoin from PreBit to your external wallet, your account need to get verified. Here is the instruction to verify your account:\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 1:</strong> Click on My Profile in the drop-down menu at the top right corner\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Step 2:</strong> Navigate to Verification Documents tab and upload your Passport/Identification Card and a picture of you selfie with Bitway or holding your Passport/Identification Card\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'How do I verify my account?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-verify-my-account', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:54:12', '2017-03-22 05:54:12', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=152', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
