(145, 1, '2017-03-20 08:15:48', '2017-03-20 08:15:48', 'The maximum amount you can distribute to the community is 10 BTC per SH/GH cycle for normal PreBit accounts (minimum SH amount is 0.05 BTC). Depending on your level, you can invest up to 100 BTC per SH/GH cycle.', 'What is the maximum SH/Deposit Amount?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-the-maximum-sh-amount', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:55:57', '2017-03-22 05:55:57', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=145', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2017-03-20 08:15:59', '2017-03-20 08:15:59', 'Tokens work like transaction fees and they are needed when you Invest/Withdraw. Each time you Invest or Withdraw, tokens will be deducted from your Token Balance. The number of tokens needed are based on the amount you Invest/Withdraw. You will need to buy some Tokens before you Send Help. Take a look at the table below for more details:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table class=\"table no-margin table-striped\" style=\"height: 191px;\" width=\"781\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\" width=\"50%\">Investment Amount</th>\r\n<th>Token Needed</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">0.05 BTC – 2.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1 Token</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">2.x BTC – 4.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td>2 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">4.x BTC – 6.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td>3 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">6.x BTC – 8.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">4 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">8.x BTC – 12.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">5 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">12.x BTC – 15.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">6 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table class=\"table no-margin table-striped\" style=\"height: 191px;\" width=\"781\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\" width=\"50%\">Withdrawal Amount</th>\r\n<th>Token Needed</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1 BTC – 3.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">1 Token</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">3.x BTC – 6.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td>2 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">6.x BTC – 9.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td>3 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">9.x BTC – 12.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">4 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">12.x BTC – 20.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">5 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">20.x BTC – 30.0 BTC</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">6 Tokens</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'What are Tokens used for?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-are-tokens-used-for', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:55:25', '2017-03-22 05:55:25', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=146', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
