(143, 1, '2017-03-20 08:14:55', '2017-03-20 08:14:55', 'As a PreBit member, you are provided with a Bitcoin wallet (it can be called PreBit wallet) linked to blockchain.info. Any outstanding balance in this wallet can be withdrawn at anytime. You can either withdraw BTC from this Bitway wallet to your external Bitcoin wallet(s) or use cash withdraw function to have the money sent directly to your bank account.', 'When can I withdraw my BTC from PreBit?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'when-i-can-withdraw-my-btc-from-prebit', '', '', '2017-03-22 05:57:48', '2017-03-22 05:57:48', '', 0, 'http://bitway.org/?post_type=faq&#038;p=143', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
